{"tid":422840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［支語呢？］無綫建議粵語新聞提供手語傳譯 通訊局接納 明年7月起實施","createTime":"2017-10-03T11:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T04:00:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"121260951a34efa21af9f46e5e3fae82c79d205b","tid":422840,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"綫的本地免費電視節目服務牌照相關規定，指示無線須由2018年7月3日起，在明珠台每日播放提供手語傳譯的粵語新聞節目。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局指，留意到聽障人士對新聞節目提供手語傳譯的需求日增，決定在兩年前生效的無綫續期牌照中加入賦權條文，加入提供手語傳譯的條文。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>通訊局表示，無綫建議在其綜合英語頻道（即明珠台）而非綜合粵語頻道（即翡翠台）提供設有手語傳譯的粵語新聞節目。通訊局負責研究手語傳譯的專責小組認為，明珠台和翡翠台的覆蓋範圍及滲透率相同，決定接納無綫的建議。</strong><br />\n<br />\n通訊局今日向無綫發出指令，規定無綫須於明年7月3日起，每日下午6時至午夜12時之間，在明珠台播放一個不少於15分鐘，設有手語傳譯及繁體中文字幕的詳盡粵語新聞節目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB-%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B47%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E9%A0%88%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%89%8B%E8%AA%9E%E5%82%B3%E8%AD%AF%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB-%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B47%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%25A0%2588%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25AA%259E%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25AD%25AF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F&d=0h42LnngE9u5w8NSj%2FaLYsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=8bb0d5fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB-%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B47%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%25A0%2588%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25AA%259E%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25AD%25AF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F&h=3ca95045\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB-%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B47%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E9%A0%88%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%89%8B%E8%AA%9E%E5%82%B3%E8%AD%AF%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/</a><br />\n<br />\n製造外語形象？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598bf2ac2f9b230f50be67aba587058e4bdea5d7","tid":422840,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:56:33.000Z","msg":"字幕唔夠？"},{"pid":"4650cc45846a64bb7ef19b9889bc2ad1bcee9d1c","tid":422840,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>字幕唔夠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n他們有些唔識字"}]}